Version 0.2
-----------

Under development.

- Supports that using dictionaries as a ``rating_group`` to choose specific
  player's rating simply.
- Changes the interface for the unity with `Elo`_ and `Glicko`_ library:

  - Adding :func:`rate_1vs1` a shortcut to rate 2 players individual match.
  - :meth:`TrueSkill.transform_ratings` is now called :meth:`TrueSkill.rate`
  - :meth:`TrueSkill.match_quality` is now called :meth:`TrueSkill.quality`

.. _Elo: http://packages.python.org/elo
.. _Glicko: http://packages.python.org/glicko

Version 0.1.4
-------------

Released on Oct 5th 2012.

Fixes :exc:`ZeroDivisionError` issue. For more detail, see `issue#3`_

.. _issue#3: https://github.com/sublee/trueskill/issues/3

Version 0.1.3
